Limpopo is leading in the registration of senior citizens for COVID-19 vaccinations. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Limpopo is leading in the registration of senior citizens for COVID-19 vaccinations. That's compared with Gauteng, Western Cape, Eastern Cape and KwaZulu-Natal. READ: COVID-19 vaccine: Ramping up the rollout Limpopo Health MEC Phophi Ramathuba says they identified the challenges in rural areas. They put up three ways for people to register and sent care workers to go door-to-door to helpe those who could not do things electronically.